{
  "stem": "11671.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so she decided, OK, I'm taking this photo album and bring that to the neighbor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we came back, we found it, that she had the photo album and the three dresses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's about the only thing that we have left from before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The pictures, and her-- it was her photo album.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it doesn't have many pictures of us in it because first of all, we didn't take many pictures because my parents wouldn't let us take pictures anyway.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my sister in the Zionist youth group did take pictures and had a lot of her group, her friends in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have one picture in it with my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm probably 14, sitting in the park reading with my sister, Yaffa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the only picture that I have of my early childhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we went been back to Cluj?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed about, I would say, about two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you said there was a shelter there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we, we had shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were orphans of the war and survivors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put in the shelter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That shelter, I don't know who it was run by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, the shelters where run by the Jewish agency and help from overseas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and we-- this was called a shelter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on they were called DP camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when they were run by the Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
